 <% include ./partials/top %>      
	<main id="about-us">
		<div class="banner">
			<h1>About us</h1>
		</div>
		<section class="intro">
			<div class="main">
				<div class="secondary content-box">
					<div class="header">
                        <h2>WHAT IS ZUPPLYCHAIN?</h2>
                    </div>
					<div class="main">
						<p>Zupplychain is a brand new concept – a dynamic marketplace to match empty warehouse space to potential storage users. 
							Whether you have a completely empty warehouse, or a few spare aisles; whether you have available space for a month or a year. Zupplychain enables you to find new customers who need your space!
							Whether you have outgrown your own storage resources, or have a seasonal or unplanned peak in requirements, or want to store your product closer to customers. Zupplychain can help you find space to match your requirements!
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="columns six">
						<div class="secondary content-box">
							<div class="header">
								<h3>PROVIDERS</h3>
							</div>
							<div class="main row">
								<p class="columns eight">Our providers of warehouse space simply register an account and list the type of space they have, how many pallet spaces they have available, and their pricing.</p>
								<div class="columns four">
									<img src="/images/provider-icon.png" alt="Zupplychain Providers"/>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="columns six">
						<div class="secondary content-box">
							<div class="header">
								<h3>USERS</h3>
							</div>
							<div class="main">
								<p class="columns eight">Potential users can search in and around any location by specifying the type and quantity of pallets they have to store. Our algorithm matches the best fits on our database; these can be sorted by price, location or quality rating.</p>
								<div class="columns four">
									<img src="/images/user-icon.png" alt="Zupplychain Users"/>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="service">
			<div class="header curved">
				<h2>Our unique service</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="main">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="service-box columns four">
						<div class="service-image">
							<img src="/images/match-icon.png" alt="Instant Matching"/>
						</div>
						<div class="service-info">
							<h3>Instant Matching</h3>
							<p>Instant matching up of detailed requirements with appropriate available space. No time wasted researching dead ends.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="service-box columns four">
						<div class="service-image">
							<img src="/images/quote-icon.png" alt="Upfront quotes"/>
						</div>
						<div class="service-info">
							<h3>Upfront quotes</h3>
							<p>Full transparency of available space and pricing.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="service-box columns four">
						<div class="service-image">
							<img src="/images/tracking-icon.png" alt="Online tracking"/>
						</div>
						<div class="service-info">
							<h3>Online tracking</h3>
							<p>On-line management system, coupled with pallet barcodes, to track each pallet and request its further movement.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="row">
					<div class="service-box columns four offset-by-two">
						<div class="service-image">
							<img src="/images/uptodate-icon.png" alt="Up-to date info"/>
						</div>
						<div class="service-info">
							<h3>Up-to date info</h3>
							<p>Fully automated communications between providers and users. No need for phone calls, meetings, etc.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="service-box columns four">
						<div class="service-image">
							<img src="/images/rating-icon.png" alt="Rating system"/>
						</div>
						<div class="service-info">
							<h3>Rating system</h3>
							<p>User and provider ratings.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="how-it-works">
			<div class="header curved">
				<h2>How it works</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="main">
				<div class="secondary content-box">
					<div class="header">
                        <h2>Register Warehouse space</h2>
                    </div>
					<div class="main row">
						<ol class="columns eight">
							<li><span>Register an account.
							<li><span>Provide basic details on the warehouse (additional warehouses can be added later).</span></li>
							<li><span>Upload photos and documents to help demonstrate your quality and service.</span></li>
							<li><span>Detail your warehouse specification by type of space, how much space in total, how many pallet spaces are available for Zupplychain users, and your pricing per week and ‘in and out’.</span></li>
							<li><span>Different pricing and availability for future periods can be stated, up to 52 weeks.</span></li>
							<li><span>Specify relevant contacts with e-mail addresses.</span></li>
							<li><span>Update your availability and pricing whenever it changes.</span></li>
							<li><span>Respond to enquiries from potential users within 48 hours.</span></li>
						</ol>
						<div class="columns four">
							<img src="/images/register-screen.png" alt="Register Warehouse space"/>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="secondary content-box">
					<div class="header">
                        <h2>Search for warehouse space</h2>
                    </div>
					<div class="main row">
						<ol class="columns eight">
							<li><span>Specify, as a minimum, where you want to space and how many pallets you have to store.</span></li>
							<li><span>Press SEARCH!</span></li>
							<li><span>Review initial search results. Fine tune search by specifying enquiry in more detail.</span></li>
							<li><span>Select a potential supplier and review its profile in detail.</span></li>
							<li><span>To confirm an enquiry with a provider, register an account and send your enquiry. The provider will respond within 48hours to confirm availability.</span></li>
						</ol>
						<div class="columns four">
							<img src="/images/search-screen.png" alt="Search for warehouse space"/>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
 <% include ./partials/bottom %>   